      "writtenOn": "2026-05-04T20:11:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We will never support boost::coroutines in this repo.  We never should\u0027ve supported them in sdbusplus in the first place.\n\nCertainly we will not be enabling them in nvidia-gpu, as they cause performance and maintenance issues.",
      "revId": "cf7c959cc3ce1512ab52957fb6aa88ca8810b280",
